title: Happy to join Venture DAO to contribute tech expertise and support growth of Ethereum ecosystem. My LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/ialferov

🌶  Motivation for joining Venture DAO   🌶     Next to my obsession with Web3 products I have for many years had a dedicated interest in crypto investment and trading. Joining Venture DAO is a natural progression for me to step up these efforts while engaging on a learningful and exciting journey with other dedicated and likeminded nerds. I’m super motivated to get my hands dirty and dedicate my time to the quest of pushing Venture DAO forward as the de facto pioneer in Web3 investment. I truly believe my contributions will enable the DAO to prosper while also providing good stories for my grandkids. 👨‍👩‍👦  Bio https://www.gustav.tech/  👨‍👩‍👦   With a background in software startups, Gus started working on Web3 projects in 2016 and has since then co-founded Linkdrop, the Community Currency Alliance and led fundraising & product efforts at Raiden and Trustlines. Gus has also won first prizes at a number of blockchain hackathons including IDEO, Blockchain for Social Impact and Devcon 3 as well as has written two peer-reviewed journal articles on blockchain technology. On the side Gus is today actively advising social impact projects, startups, associations and investment funds.
